how do you lite a rheem pilot lite u shoud have a red knob black if its propane on top of ur thermostat turn the dial to the right of that until pilot lines up with the arrow on front then push then red or black button down then if its a newer heater u should have a red igniter button just push it down and u will hear it click if so look in the peep hole under that valve and see if the pilot is lit if so then hold the button doen for secs then release slowly watchign to make sure the pilots stays on if so ur good if not just repeat until it stays on if u dont have a new style and u have to manually lit it urself u have to put ur hand in the chamber and light the pilot like that if u dont know how i would suggest calling a plumber to light it for u good luck Thermostat Furnace Diving regulator Diesel engine Drag racing Bi-metal Internal ballistics Dance Dance Revolution EXTREME 2000 Australian Grand Prix M16 (rifle) Thermocouple Carburetor Two-stroke cycle VHF omnidirectional range Bong Pump It Up Flight Unlimited II Dance Dance Revolution EXTREME (North America) Curling Space Shuttle Solid Rocket Booster Yu-Gi-Oh! Trading Card Game Hot air balloon Firearm Portable stove DDRMAX: Dance Dance Revolution Mercury 4 Team Fortress Classic Spark plug Honda Prelude DDRMAX2: Dance Dance Revolution 7thMIX Archery IPod Thermal power station The Time Machine Dance Dance Revolution The Chemical Brothers Pinball Apollo 13 Revolver Heckler & Koch G3 Bubble Bobble Dance Dance Revolution ULTRAMIX DDRMAX2: Dance Dance Revolution Prank flash Knight Rider Mario Aaliyah Fountain pen Dance Dance Revolution ULTRAMIX 2 Switch Technology in the Stargate universe Sega Saturn Lighter Air traffic control Light switch 2005 European Grand Prix Beretta 92F/FS Manual transmission IMac B-47 Stratojet Suplex Aerial (dance move) Shirt Resident Evil (video game) Nintendo GameCube Nintendo DS Palm OS Beatmania IIDX Professional wrestling throws Tag Water heater Refrigerator The Legend of Zelda: The Mini